<paragraph blockId="46.[151,1436,1634,1700]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,326,1634,1660]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Observations:</emphasis>
After morphological comparisons, 
<bibRefCitation author="Abdala" box="[766,991,1634,1660]" firstAuthor="Abdala" page="39" pageId="46" pageNumber="47" pagination="1 - 84" refId="ref50199" refString="Abdala, C. S. (2007) Phylogeny of the boulengeri group (Iguania: Liolaemidae, Liolaemus) based on morphological and molecular characters. Zootaxa, 1538, 1 - 84." type="journal article" year="2007">Abdala (2007: 39)</bibRefCitation>
